title: Persia
author: NovaCeasar
pages:
#- 3 months ago, MTA decided to take over Persia and why shouldn't they? All Persia is now is an abandoned city now, but that wasn't always like that. §0
§0
§0Let's take a path down my memory lane to the start of Devoted. I've been playing for 2 weeks now and have
#- settled in a small hidy hole with my friend Garking. Although theres 2 of us I seemed to do all the work with Gar only being able to play on the weekends. With this being so, I decided to buy some titanium and mercury and who did I choose to trade with? §0

#- None other then Saren_Solaris. we started to regularly meet up and trade so much that at 1000 2000 we made the "S.S Trading Post".
#- 